Line13.136591: Hmm. A friend was supposed to meet me here. I worry that she may have been detained.
Line15.136591: It’s risky to show my face on the street with all the knights out there. Could you have a look around for me?

Line9.136591: Well, if it isn’t the desert wanderer. No worse for wear, I see. That drink I owe you will have to wait. I don’t suppose you saw an old woman in the street outside just now, did you?
